Viewed this last night and don't agree with Leto.

Don't think he actually D/L'd it even, just interested in diverting people to the wrestling tracker.

Quality is fine, equal to one of the better weekly show (+-)700MB XviD encodings, not blocky and perfectly enjoyable with no wrestlers movements missed from low quality, sound ok etc.

What one expects from a PDTV release in fact and i've seen a couple of HDTV which were below par occasionally but PDTV is very consistant.

Thanks again for the upload amanrulz  matey, arrrrrrrr. : )
